{"tid":1495241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"觀察：近期中共及香港傀儡政府奏起的主旋律","createTime":"2019-08-22T03:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T03:39:59.000Z","uid":152313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"221bb70ee947ac57ce252594fb32661c6f8c744f","tid":1495241,"uid":152313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:39:14.000Z","msg":"睇有線中國組報導，環時呼籲<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">恢復香港秩序</span></span></strong>，想用拖字訣同扮無野，淡化香港反送中示威；而最近兩次示威，黑警都無出催淚彈，同環時所講嘅互相呼應。<br />\n<br />\n有呢個情況，估計同美國積極介入有關，尤其是美國9月復會傾美國香港民主法。<br />\n<br />\n手足們，抖咗一個星期，回氣未？大家智仁勇並存，應該知來緊點做。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2224506641027143&amp;id=265944843550009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2224506641027143%26id%3D265944843550009&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=faad532d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2224506641027143&amp;id=265944843550009</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">【香港「和理非」遊行　內地官方輿論如何回應？】\n\n香港818沒有催淚彈、衝擊和流血的遊行，內地傳媒的關注點在哪？\n\n而《環球時報》社評分析，「暴力退場」的主因原來是...\n\n#818\n#和理非遊行\n#有線中國組\n</code></pre>"},{"pid":"0ad0c6cff261488e0ad4dd05fab89e4c73648070","tid":1495241,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:39:59.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU，而家搭車犯法呀?</strong></span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrRtRqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrRtRqw